{"tid":442572,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【繁體支那】台灣女官扯獎牌 世界冠軍單車手被迫彎腰","createTime":"2017-10-20T17:46:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-20T23:29:10.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"e061d88c775b3da605e6af754e9dc215e9429128","tid":442572,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T17:46:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/china/20171020/57357388\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fchina%2F20171020%2F57357388&d=HvnfUf5OLwwsvTyJ8D7oaU%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=22311f28\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fchina%2F20171020%2F57357388&h=ab681740\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/china/20171020/57357388</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20171020/large/1508505200_70f0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171020%2Flarge%2F1508505200_70f0.jpg&h=6867a651&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2017年台灣自行車登山王挑戰（Taiwan KOM Challenge）今日從花蓮七星潭出發至合歡山武嶺，總長105公里，海拔落差3,275米，結束後頒獎時卻發生頒獎人、交通部觀光局副局長陳淑慧為了合照，扯住金牌騎士、意大利名將倪巴利（Vincenzo Nibali）獎牌帶，讓倪巴利只能維持彎腰鞠躬姿勢窘態，雖僅約10秒，但在BBS上引發網民批評，稱她像牽着動物一樣。<br />\n<br />\n各種網路意見包括「勒頸魔」、「太丟臉了」、「旁邊的選手覺得慶幸沒得獎」、「大媽果然不分國界」、「這腦袋到底在想甚麼啊」及「未免太不尊重選手」。<br />\n<br />\n陳淑慧後來在頒發銀牌時未再有銅牌舉動，頒發銅牌時則還是勾住獎牌帶下緣，只是因為頒獎台銅牌位置高度比金牌位置低不少，選手仍可站立與她合照。<br />\n<br />\n倪巴利在自由車公路3大賽都曾奪冠，2010年拿下環西班牙賽總冠軍，2013、16年拿下環意大利賽總冠軍，2014年環法國賽也獲總冠軍。<br />\n<br />\n台灣《蘋果日報》／東森新聞雲"},{"pid":"306b31c22fb54b19750f9f403b5550e5d18c12d4","tid":442572,"uid":52323,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T17:48:50.000Z","msg":"nibali咁好脾氣"},{"pid":"cd2c63b5a632e95f470fdd97c51fbc7a47c83c45","tid":442572,"uid":29080,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T17:54:29.000Z","msg":"當人狗"},{"pid":"349c96b8ca9e4946e12